Step1:

MuseSDK Tools 3.4.1
https://sites.google.com/a/interaxon.ca/muse-developer-site/download

Step2:

Liblo (and its dependencies Automake, Libtool, Autoconf)
Cython
pyliblo

provided you have homebrew and pip, install for step 2 goes like:
(brew install liblo also takes care of automake, libtool, and autoconf)
$ brew install liblo
$ pip install cython
$ pip install pyliblo

Step4: Visuals
Processing https://processing.org/

Step5: Beads audio library
Take from introspection/src and copy into your Processing Library folder (found by opening processing and hitting preferences)